title: Kenneth Rodman, 'missing' five years, in wrong place at wrong time
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › Kenneth Rodman, 'missing' five years,... Kenneth Rodman, 'missing' five years, in wrong place at wrong time Next Story Prev Story 2 hrs ago Read more: The Age 
After nearly five years laying low in Far North Queensland, Kenneth Rodman must have thought he had successfully staged the perfect disappearing act. And the American tourist just might have had it not been for an almost implausible collision of timing that led to his capture last week. Start the conversation, or Read more at The Age.
